nd positive correlations between participants'\npersonality traits, Godspeed Questionnaire subscales, and the average approach\ndistance. The technical contribution of this work is the real-time perception\nof 25 keypoints on the human body using a single compact RGB-D camera and the\nuse of these points for accurate interpersonal distance estimation and as\ngazing targets for the robot.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Sep 2020 17:34:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-04"}
