 $U/t$. A comparison of the square and triangular\nlattice reveals the additional effect of geometric frustration on damping.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 3 Sep 2020 17:56:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 14 Dec 2021 08:03:39 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-12-16"}
