o derive a general formula for Bredon\ncohomological dimension for a group $G$ admitting a cocompact model for\n$E_{\\mathcal{F}}G$. As a consequence of both, we obtain a simple formula for\nproper cohomological dimension of $\\mathrm{CAT}(0)$ groups whose actions admit\na strict fundamental domain.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 4 Sep 2020 12:48:40 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Fri, 7 Oct 2022 13:28:14 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-10-10"}
